data.description: Unbelievable!! 2+ Acres in the City Limits? Yes! This Open Airy floorplan has 3 bed, 2 bath and has just been updated with Fresh Paint inside and out, new main bathroom and tough wood plank vinyl flooring! Roof and gutters are just 6 years old! Oversized 2 car garage, expansive patio can also be used as carport, and a garden area that is fenced in to keep the critters out. Cement Driveway runs all the way to the shop. A little bit of work on the shop and you have a great place for whatever you can dream up. Plenty of room to expand.  Room for a shop, Horse Barn, and more! Perk!! Most of the acreage is on water frontage! Seller is offering Buyer's 2 for 1 Buyers Rate Buy Down up to 10,200.00
